document_data.Notable Owners:
*[[Kordin|Alley Cat Kordin]], a cat burglar in [[Tantras]], owned a pair. The ''slippers'' did little to aid his career, as he was both extremely clumsy and unlucky.{{Cite card/AD&D Trading Cards/1992|347|Alley Cat Kordin}}
*[[Orlpar Husteem]], a [[Waterdeep|Waterdhavian]] noble and drug dealer.{{Cite dungeon/126/Vampires of Waterdeep: Blood of Malar|67}}
*[[Paelinn]], a [[drow]] [[divine seeker]] of [[Kiaransalee]] in [[Maerimydra]].
*[[Pallandra]], a [[cleric|high priestess]] of [[Set]] in [[Mulhorand]].{{Cite card/AD&D Trading Cards/1991|320|Pallandra}}
*[[Ryngoth]], an ex-[[Red Wizard of Thay]] and the High Priest of [[Kya Mordrayn]]'s cell of the [[Cult of the Dragon]] stationed in the [[Tower of Bones]], [[Polyandrium]] of [[Myth Drannor]] in [[1369 DR]].
